2D shape Hierarchy

Object
    - Shape
        - Polygon
            - Line
            - Triangle n = 3
                - Isosceles
                    - Equilateral
            - Quadrilateral n = 4
                - Rectangle
                - Parallelogram
                    - Rhombus
                        - Square
                    - Rectangle
                        - Square
                - Trapezoid
                - Square
            - Pentagon n = 5
            - Hexagon n = 6
            - Heptagon n = 7
            - etc
        - Oval
            - Circle
        - Arc


